{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/contact/layout,_N_T_/contact/page,_N_T_/contact"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/0a2f060a962c327f.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-616e068a201ad621.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/fd9d1056-3eee857bde8f3b06.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/117-e6f8effb6353785e.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-aa40221319a8983c.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/contact/page-3b3e131c27ffdc2d.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/972-ceea3baa05359a1c.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-9e07af492dbe15bf.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>EIE SA — Enough Is Enough South Africa</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Youth-led civil society movement committed to accountability, transparency, and good governance. Enough Is Enough South Africa.\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\"><div class=\"bg-brand-red text-white text-center font-bold uppercase tracking-wide py-2 px-4 text-xs relative\"><span>🔴 UPCOMING: EIE SA × IEC Online Voter Education Workshop — 2026 LGE — Top 8 Political Parties Participating.<!-- --> <a href=\"https://forms.gle/E8VVXN12KRKZhBsV6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors\">TARGET: 100+ YOUTH — CLICK HERE TO JOIN →</a></span><button class=\"absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-white/70 hover:text-white text-base font-normal\" aria-label=\"Dismiss\">×</button></div><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-brand-charcoal border-b-2 border-brand-red\"><nav class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"font-oswald text-xl font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-white\" href=\"/\">EIE <span class=\"text-brand-red\">SA</span></a><ul class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-1 list-none\"><li><a class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase px-4 py-2 rounded-sm transition-all duration-150 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase px-4 py-2 rounded-sm transition-all duration-150 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10\" href=\"/campaigns\">Campaigns</a></li><li><a class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase px-4 py-2 rounded-sm transition-all duration-150 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10\" href=\"/join\">Join Us</a></li><li><a class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase px-4 py-2 rounded-sm transition-all duration-150 bg-brand-red text-white\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li></ul><a class=\"hidden md:block btn-red text-xs rounded-sm\" href=\"/join\">Join the Movement</a><button class=\"md:hidden flex flex-col gap-1.5 p-2\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-white transition-all duration-200 \"></span><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-white transition-all duration-200 \"></span><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-white transition-all duration-200 \"></span></button></nav></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"page-hero\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"color:#ef4444\">Get in Touch</div><h1 class=\"font-oswald font-bold uppercase text-white leading-none tracking-tight\" style=\"font-size:clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem)\">Contact <span class=\"text-brand-red\">EIE SA</span></h1><p class=\"text-gray-400 mt-4 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">For partnerships, media enquiries, donation information, or to find out how to get involved in your province.</p></div></div><section class=\"section-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16\"><div><div class=\"eyebrow\">Direct Contact</div><h2 class=\"font-oswald text-2xl font-bold uppercase text-brand-black mb-6\">Reach Us <span class=\"text-brand-red\">Directly</span></h2><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 mb-2\">Email</div><a href=\"mailto:enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com\" class=\"text-brand-red text-sm hover:underline break-all\">enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com</a><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1\">For press enquiries, include MEDIA in the subject line.</p></div><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 mb-2\">Website</div><a href=\"https://www.eiesa.org.za\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"text-brand-red text-sm hover:underline\">www.eiesa.org.za</a></div><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 mb-3\">Social Media</div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><a href=\"https://x.com/eiesouthafrica?s=21\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center gap-3 py-2 border-b border-gray-100 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150 group\"><span class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-black group-hover:text-brand-red w-24 flex-shrink-0 transition-colors duration-150\">X / Twitter</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\">@eiesouthafrica</span></a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/1EF3WwRFfU/?mibextid=wwXIfr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center gap-3 py-2 border-b border-gray-100 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150 group\"><span class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-black group-hover:text-brand-red w-24 flex-shrink-0 transition-colors duration-150\">Facebook</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\">EIE SA</span></a><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/eie_sa?igsh=MTFzYWpyZXhqczJhYw==\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center gap-3 py-2 border-b border-gray-100 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150 group\"><span class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-black group-hover:text-brand-red w-24 flex-shrink-0 transition-colors duration-150\">Instagram</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\">@eie_sa</span></a><a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@enoughisenough_sa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center gap-3 py-2 border-b border-gray-100 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150 group\"><span class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-black group-hover:text-brand-red w-24 flex-shrink-0 transition-colors duration-150\">TikTok</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\">@enoughisenough_sa</span></a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center gap-3 py-2 border-b border-gray-100 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150 group\"><span class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-black group-hover:text-brand-red w-24 flex-shrink-0 transition-colors duration-150\">LinkedIn</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\">EIE SA</span></a></div></div><div class=\"bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-brand-red p-4\"><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-red mb-1\">Media Enquiries</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">For press, interviews, or media partnerships, contact us by email with <strong>MEDIA</strong> in the subject line.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><div class=\"eyebrow\">Send a Message</div><h2 class=\"font-oswald text-2xl font-bold uppercase text-brand-black mb-6\">Get in <span class=\"text-brand-red\">Touch</span></h2><div class=\"bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-6 text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">You can also email us directly at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com\" class=\"text-brand-red font-semibold hover:underline\">enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com</a>. We respond to all enquiries within 2 to 3 business days.</div><form noValidate=\"\"><div class=\"mb-5\"><label for=\"cname\" class=\"block font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-2\">Your Name <span class=\"text-brand-red\">*</span></label><input id=\"cname\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Full name\" class=\"w-full bg-white border text-brand-black text-sm px-4 py-3 outline-none transition-colors duration-150 border-gray-200 focus:border-brand-red\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"mb-5\"><label for=\"csubject\" class=\"block font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-2\">Subject <span class=\"text-brand-red\">*</span></label><select id=\"csubject\" class=\"w-full bg-white border text-brand-black text-sm px-4 py-3 outline-none transition-colors duration-150 appearance-none border-gray-200 focus:border-brand-red\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Select a subject...</option><option value=\"General Enquiry\">General Enquiry</option><option value=\"Media / Press\">Media / Press</option><option value=\"Partnership Proposal\">Partnership Proposal</option><option value=\"Volunteer / Join\">Volunteer / Join</option><option value=\"Donation\">Donation</option><option value=\"Legal / Advocacy\">Legal / Advocacy</option><option value=\"IEC Workshop Registration\">IEC Workshop Registration</option></select></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><label for=\"cmessage\" class=\"block font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-2\">Message <span class=\"text-brand-red\">*</span></label><textarea id=\"cmessage\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"How can we help you?\" class=\"w-full bg-white border text-brand-black text-sm px-4 py-3 outline-none transition-colors duration-150 resize-vertical border-gray-200 focus:border-brand-red\"></textarea></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full font-oswald font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm text-white py-4 transition-all duration-150 bg-brand-red hover:bg-brand-red-dark\">Send Message</button></form></div></div></section><section class=\"section-charcoal\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center\"><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-gray-400 mb-3\">Community</div><h2 class=\"font-oswald font-bold uppercase text-white leading-tight mb-4\" style=\"font-size:clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem)\">Join the EIE SA <span class=\"text-brand-red\">WhatsApp Community</span></h2><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Get real-time updates, civic education content, campaign announcements, and direct access to the EIE SA community — straight to your WhatsApp.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-6 list-none\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400\"><span class=\"text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\">→</span>Campaign updates and action alerts</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400\"><span class=\"text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\">→</span>Ward councillor accountability tools and resources</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400\"><span class=\"text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\">→</span>IEC registration reminders ahead of 2026 LGE</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400\"><span class=\"text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\">→</span>Direct community engagement with EIE SA leadership</li></ul><a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/C8yjZDtKyJPHk4OFGGRQz0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block font-oswald font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm text-white bg-brand-black border border-white/20 px-6 py-3 transition-all duration-150 hover:bg-brand-red hover:border-brand-red\">📲 Join WhatsApp Community →</a></div><div class=\"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 text-center\"><div class=\"text-6xl mb-4\">💬</div><div class=\"font-oswald text-lg font-bold uppercase text-white mb-2\">Active Community</div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">Join thousands of South Africans demanding accountability, civic education, and electoral reform.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"section-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"eyebrow\">Independent Funding</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Grassroots <span class=\"text-brand-red\">Support</span></h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mt-8 items-start\"><div><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6\">EIE SA relies entirely on grassroots support and strategic partnerships. We accept no funding that compromises our independence. Every contribution — large or small — directly funds civic education, campaign materials, legal advocacy, and community outreach.</p><div class=\"bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-6 mb-6\"><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-4\">Financial Transparency Commitment</div><ul class=\"space-y-3 list-none\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0\">📊</span>Quarterly financial reports published publicly</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0\">🔍</span>Annual external audits — results made public</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0\">🏛️</span>Dedicated financial governance committee</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0\">📋</span>Full income and expenditure breakdowns</li></ul></div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">For direct bank transfer details or grant and partnership enquiries, contact us at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com\" class=\"text-brand-red hover:underline\">enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com</a></p></div><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-4\">Contribution Channels</div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"border border-dashed border-gray-200 p-5 flex items-center justify-between bg-gray-50\"><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-sm font-bold uppercase text-gray-400 mb-0.5\">GoFundMe</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Crowdfunding campaign — coming soon</div></div><span class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-300 border border-dashed border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 flex-shrink-0 ml-4\">Coming Soon</span></div><div class=\"border border-dashed border-gray-200 p-5 flex items-center justify-between bg-gray-50\"><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-sm font-bold uppercase text-gray-400 mb-0.5\">PayPal</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Direct international contributions — coming soon</div></div><span class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-300 border border-dashed border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 flex-shrink-0 ml-4\">Coming Soon</span></div><div class=\"border border-gray-200 p-5 flex items-center justify-between group hover:border-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\"><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-sm font-bold uppercase text-brand-black mb-0.5\">Bank Transfer (EFT)</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">South African bank transfer — contact us for details</div></div><a href=\"mailto:enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com?subject=Donation Enquiry\" class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-red border border-brand-red px-4 py-2 hover:bg-brand-red hover:text-white transition-all duration-150 flex-shrink-0 ml-4\">Contact →</a></div><div class=\"border border-gray-200 p-5 flex items-center justify-between group hover:border-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\"><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-sm font-bold uppercase text-brand-black mb-0.5\">Grants &amp; Partnerships</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Organisations supporting democracy &amp; governance reform</div></div><a href=\"mailto:enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com?subject=Partnership Proposal\" class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-red border border-brand-red px-4 py-2 hover:bg-brand-red hover:text-white transition-all duration-150 flex-shrink-0 ml-4\">Enquire →</a></div></div><div class=\"mt-6 bg-gray-50 border border-dashed border-gray-300 p-5 text-center\"><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2\">Quarterly Audit Tracker</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">Financial reports and audit results will be published here quarterly. Transparency is not optional — it is our commitment to every contributor.</p><div class=\"mt-3 inline-block font-oswald text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-300 border border-dashed border-gray-300 px-3 py-1.5\">Coming Q1 2026</div></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-brand-charcoal text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-14 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 border-b border-white/10\"><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-xl font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3\">EIE <span class=\"text-brand-red\">SA</span></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-xs\">Enough Is Enough South Africa is a youth-led civil society movement committed to accountability, transparency, and good governance. We refuse to inherit a broken nation.</p></div><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-gray-500 mb-4\">Navigate</div><ul class=\"space-y-2 list-none\"><li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/campaigns\">Campaigns</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/join\">Join Us</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/join\">Join / Donate</a></li></ul></div><div><div class=\"font-oswald text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-gray-500 mb-4\">Connect</div><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400 list-none\"><li><a href=\"https://x.com/eiesouthafrica?s=21\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"hover:text-brand-red transition-colors\">X / Twitter — @eiesouthafrica</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/1EF3WwRFfU/?mibextid=wwXIfr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"hover:text-brand-red transition-colors\">Facebook — EIE SA</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/eie_sa?igsh=MTFzYWpyZXhqczJhYw==\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"hover:text-brand-red transition-colors\">Instagram — @eie_sa</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@enoughisenough_sa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"hover:text-brand-red transition-colors\">TikTok — @enoughisenough_sa</a></li><li><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-brand-red transition-colors\">LinkedIn — EIE SA</a></li><li><a href=\"mailto:enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com\" class=\"hover:text-brand-red transition-colors\">enoughisenoughaone@gmail.com</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"max-w-6xl